data.eml:eml: New species of Blaesodactylus (Squamata: Gekkonidae) from Tsingy karstic outcrops in Ankarana National Park, northern Madagascar

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Jono, Teppei, Bauer, Aaron M., Brennan, Ian, Mori, Akira (2015): New species of Blaesodactylus (Squamata: Gekkonidae) from Tsingy karstic outcrops in Ankarana National Park, northern Madagascar. Zootaxa 3980 (3): 406-416, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3980.3.4
